SCHEMA: governance/testx_suites.schema
schema_id: dominium.schema.governance.testx_suites
schema_version: 1.0.0
stability: core

PURPOSE:
- Define TestX suite tiers and deterministic execution constraints.
- Allow manifest-driven selective execution for fast lanes.

STABILITY GUARANTEES:
- Required fields MUST exist.
- Unknown extension keys MUST be preserved.
- No field removal/rename without MAJOR version bump.

NON-SEMANTICS:
- Suite policy governs validation orchestration only.
- It does not alter simulation semantics.

REQUIRED SHAPE:
record testx_suite_registry
  required:
    - registry_id: id
    - registry_version: tag
    - schema_version_ref: tag
    - suites: [testx_suite]
    - extensions: map

record testx_suite
  required:
    - suite_id: id
    - test_tags: [tag]
    - required_gates: [id]
    - deterministic_required: bool
    - environment_constraints: [tag]
    - extensions: map
